These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
2 different games are played: snooker, bridge
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Game   | bridge     | snooker  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different games are played: snooker, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Game         | chess   | snooker      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Beverage     | juice | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | zombie |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, mexican
House: victorian, craftsman
