.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
There are 2 different nationalities: american, turkish
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
2. the american is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Nationality   | turkish | american |
| Transport     | bus   | bike    |

